f ocused on credit scores, down payments, and interest rates — which is exactly right. But many also make 
$20,000  to $70,000  mistakes driven not by a lack of  inf ormation, but by invisible psychological patterns called 
cognitive biases. 
Mo Phanor is a Licensed Mortgage Loan Originator (NMLS#  2420740),  licensed to originate mortgage loans in 
